txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Flawed ears from the beasts near Trestlebridge. Deliver the items to Guardsman Otley in the town of Trestlebridge.
'I am certain that this will be a welcome delivery. Thank you.'
'Some folks would like to continue their work and asked me to collect the ears. If you are willing to help, it would be appreciated.'
Men of Bree Task: Flawed Ears
Guardsman Otley, in Trestlebridge, is awaiting delivery of flawed ears at the war-torn town of Trestlebridge.
Deliver the flawed ears to Guardsman Otley at Trestlebridge
You have been tasked with collecting flawed ears from the beasts near Trestlebridge.\n\nYou can deliver the items to Guardsman Otley at Trestlebridge.
Wanted: Flawed ears from the beasts near Trestlebridge.
